Title: The Magic of Paris and its romance
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-magic-of-paris-and-its-romance
SetInCountry: France
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Nabila Belbachir
AuthorCountry: Algeria
Text: l remember my dans in the land of devils and angels.when l see the Eiffel tower
  l recall my adventures with the bright coloris and romance of the frensh people.when
  l smell the roses l remember the gardens of France in which we volunteered as visitors
  to pollinate flowers and plant trees.when l see the mountains l remember the days
  of snow with mu Friends and our chellenge about who first climbs the ropes .the
  city of games where l spent times when l forget the World....yes really Paris is
  a charming city
